PrecisEnactment of an ORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2000 (SKIDEGATE, SPALLUMCHEEN AND WHITECAP DAKOTA FIRST NATION BANDS) which adds three First Nation Bands to the list of Indian Bands whose Councils may make by-laws imposing a direct tax on alcoholic beverages, fuel or tobacco products.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2002-0376 Publication Date: 2002-11-06

precis: Enactment of an ORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2000 (SKIDEGATE, SPALLUMCHEEN AND WHITECAP DAKOTA FIRST NATION BANDS) which adds three First Nation Bands to the list of Indian Bands whose Councils may make by-laws imposing a direct tax on alcoholic beverages, fuel or tobacco products.
